  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Heparin Dosing Score Protocol for Polymyxin-B Hemoperfusion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Efficacy of Heparin Dosing Score Protocol for Anticoagulation During Polymyxin-B Hemoperfusion: a Retrospective Study</official_title>
